com.foreach.across.modules.entity.validators

Class EntityValidatorSupport<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.validators.EntityValidatorSupport<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.validation.SmartValidator, org.springframework.validation.Validator

    public abstract class EntityValidatorSupport<T>
extends Object
implements org.springframework.validation.SmartValidator
    Base adapter class for a custom Validator that by default applies the registered entity validator bean (named EntityModule.VALIDATOR) if there is one.

    Provides hooks to execute before and after the default validator. Supports smart validation hints and provides pre and post validation methods with and without validation hints.

    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
